{"tid":2510472,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"大手連環掃貨，買入16伙御苑","createTime":"2021-04-30T07:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:08:13.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af8c8c35c1abeedcb9ea57ed1f2f40cde0f8331f","tid":2510472,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"市場消息指，恒基旗下粉嶺高爾夫‧御苑，錄大手客由3月起連環掃貨，共購入該盤約16伙，均為8座單位，成交價共約2.5億，由於均由同一名稱登記，須繳付達樓價15%辣稅，料涉及稅項達3750萬。<br />\n<br />\n當中9伙經已註冊，位於8座中至高層A及B室，面積961至1048方呎，成交價為1482萬至1659萬，呎價由15596至15752元，買家均以個人名義登記，為趙志芬（Chiu Chi Fun）。"},{"pid":"89f49f348d62b310b98ddde7af8745d0eb7f070d","tid":2510472,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"呢個死貨盤都買16伙 係咪痴的"},{"pid":"8d245994841146b5f86c59131f8f30e4feceb4a9","tid":2510472,"uid":277759,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"掃埋啲垃圾盤 成個屋苑開售左咁耐 都唔知有冇賣左一半 有時行過地產鋪 仲見到有銀主盤出現"},{"pid":"56058be341ca4efd55a3ce1bbfcd86dce80c734a","tid":2510472,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"佢係咪見新地高價投左古洞地皮呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8173578d92a793a28c4af1acb672a9161b0ee72b","tid":2510472,"uid":101341,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d245994841146b5f86c59131f8f30e4feceb4a9","tid":2510472,"uid":277759,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"掃埋啲垃圾盤 成個屋苑開售左咁耐 都唔知有冇賣左一半 有時行過地產鋪 仲見到有銀主盤出現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔又教有錢人投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c512dfb93c4e587ed15013b9315eb4f8b71d91ec","tid":2510472,"uid":195136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89f49f348d62b310b98ddde7af8745d0eb7f070d","tid":2510472,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T